The '''Heorem Complex''', or '''SIS Headquarters''' during the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]], was a kilometer-wide collection of buildings in the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It bordered [[Quadrant H-46]] and contained the [[Heorem Skytunnel]], which connected the two sectors.

During the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], the Complex served as the headquarters of the [[Republic Strategic Information Service]], separate from the [[Strategic Information Service operations center|SIS operations center]], and contained the [[Director's office|offices]] of the [[Director of Republic Strategic Information Service|Director of SIS]].

